{
  "stem": "1160.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What I see, their legs-- I'm not watching their faces anymore, because I'm watching their legs, because their legs were going such a fast, one after another, like you take a camera, you know, and you make the video forward, back.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One after other there is-- you can't even blink how fast the feet is changing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was fascinated with this, just absolutely fascinated how a human being can run so fast.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then they reach very fast, very fast this trench there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they are starting to chase those people who were left in the-- in this ditch there, in this long ditch.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And they were running like cat and mouse.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The people with their-- with their rubber stick, of course, is the cat.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the people down there, the little mouse.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But they wanted to come out on one side, crawling, jumping up there, and you know how you like to go up.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Fall back.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "As soon as they started to crawl, there was already the stick, hitting them, screaming.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "My mother comes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She says, come away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Don't watch.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So I don't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "This is the picture, though, what I remember.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I remember a lot of walking.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I remember a terrible lot of walking.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I remember at one-- I don't know where we are walking.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But one walking, it took very long.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I'm extremely tired.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Running.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I mean, from-- I'm very tired from the walking, hungry, thirsty.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my grandmother has to be carried.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So how do you carry a person who cannot walk?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So my oldest brother and my mother, they hold their hands like this.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They hold onto each other.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my mother-- my grandmother-- three of us, we put my grandmother up on those hands.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
